abstract: Ivo Karlovic of Croatia beats Donald Young, 6-3, 6-3, to become oldest champion in 23-year history of Florida's Delray Beach Open.
lead_paragraph: Ivo Karlovic of Croatia won the Delray Beach Open to become the oldest champion in the 23-year history of the Florida tournament.

headline.main: In Florida, Ivo Karlovic Is a Champion at 35
